title: Donald Trump filmed 'rehearsing' Congress speech in his car
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Donald Trump filmed 'rehearsing' Congress speech in his car 1 March 2017 Last updated at 15:57 GMT 
President Donald Trump has been caught on camera in his car, apparently practicing his first speech to US Congress, before being driven to the Capitol building. Read more
